name: Bungo
description:
Bungo (Skull) 

Inspired by a song of local artist from PH, Kemikal Ali. He's talking on how oneself prevent to being boastful. Reminding his listeners to be grounded. 



Collecting this and other 1/1s creation means supporting a dream of the artist to continue his craft while making a living.
Join Jakestudyos on his journey and evolution.
